{"tid":2148142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度喀拉拉山泥傾瀉增至最少43死 20人仍下落不明","createTime":"2020-08-09T17:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T17:48:25.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff182a46271417585061ec22d488799b3d4e533","tid":2148142,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"印度喀拉拉山泥傾瀉增至最少43死 20人仍下落不明<br />\n2020-08-10 HKT 01:04<br />\n<br />\n&quot;印度喀拉拉邦拉賈卡德鎮上周五發生的大規模山泥傾瀉，死亡人數增至最少43人。<br />\n<br />\n搜救工作在周日繼續，救援人員在現場一帶，陸續找到17具遺體，目前仍有約20人下落不明。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542762-20200810.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542762-20200810.htm&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YqVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=c5a46f87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542762-20200810.htm&h=50282738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542762-20200810.htm</a>"},{"pid":"645a58fb19adc706b2779f1109b120f3e38abfed","tid":2148142,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TEHjHOd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEHjHOd.jpg&h=9748f897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />師傅一年前已經同我講過， 佢話「唔可以太劇烈運動，加上餵人奶要食番多啲嘢，如果唔係唔夠奶。」"},{"pid":"67f21e756e5a6a4e0026462485fb552554ea3106","tid":2148142,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:48:25.000Z","msg":"呢一年發生咩事"}]}